{"tid":1388600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【拋磚引玉】 要好好運用 張建宗 呢張牌","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:22:29.000Z","uid":198991,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf6c0d1869ec264649b82cb74c49c93ba7d2f7f","tid":1388600,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"司長出左黎認錯之後兩日就跪低左，坊間都開始同意係軍政府狀態，要好好使用呢張牌<br />\n<br />\n新口號(A)：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「軍政府狀態、差佬大撚晒」</span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\">(或：有槍就惡晒)</span><br />\n新口號(B)：<span style=\"color: red;\">「陀槍XX、司長跪低」</span> (SOR9Y 諗唔到有咩字壓韻，求巴絲幫手)<br />\n<br />\n好處有三：<br />\n<br />\n1) 除左中間/微藍公務員已經 WE CONNECT，事實上仲有其他藍絲/紀律部隊仲一直撐緊政府及警犬；始終藍絲公務員個老頂係張建宗，口號可以令1/3人唔再盲撐警犬已經好大幫助 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 老解角度：你班ON9 城管，要不要真係比你睇睇咩叫軍政府狀態？ &gt;&gt; 焦土派目標達成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3) 輸出革命：工作關係 WECHAT 有GROUP，入面班廣州仔唔知點解好關注香港，但一面倒支持城管打鳩廢青；自從城管屌鳩司長之後，問佢地係咪支持城管反政府，全場靜左好多；而呢D 敏感詞口號去到CCTV，老解自己都會諗一諗，維尼又要花時間加強教育 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望被控呢45個義士係黎明前既最後既黑暗，只要過埋呢關，曙光將會到來 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在下好少出POST，有錯屌細力D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(Verify Code : 8964)"},{"pid":"40c4a1cd4fb861cd2d7667df4b5e55c8eefd479b","tid":1388600,"uid":90515,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"聚集一班人，設路障，噴黑交通燈，去隔離街，再設路障，再噴黑交通燈，見到黑警，散水去其他區，設路障，噴黑交通燈，重復重復再重復<br />\n<br />\n原因: 以不被捕不受傷為大前題，同狗方硬碰硬係無勝算，裝備訓練各方面都輸曬。不過黑警弱點好明顯。裝備厚重、部署時期長，耐力低。每次出動至少幾個鐘，相當於一個跑唔郁嘅大隻佬。所以死守一個地方幾個鐘係無用，要以速度對抗力量<br />\n<br />\nQ. 啲狗一黎，無人守嘅路障立即被秒殺，有撚用？<br />\n<br />\nA. 路障可以即刻拆，但噴黑左嘅交通燈無得即刻處理。而且透過不停制作路障，大大增加狗方需要嘅覆蓋範圍，等於迫班防暴速龍係咁跑<br />\n<br />\n結語: 避其鋒，攻其短，絕不能再犧牲勇武派！<br />\n<br />\n利申：FF"},{"pid":"d3849be391020de93808b7231ca1241a7d94e529","tid":1388600,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"06aa1e12e90f27fa3a40506852bd8459424ca873","tid":1388600,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:36:05.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n試著說<br />\n<br />\n聽朝九點西灣河東區法院<br />\n82遮打集會<br />\n85全民罷工"},{"pid":"278803cc993616f3ae250fb5a8f5f2c2651582c1","tid":1388600,"uid":209679,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:37:43.000Z","msg":"陀槍奶閪 司長跪低"},{"pid":"ea564a2332375da144f1906b59cd78191e70f3ab","tid":1388600,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:38:23.000Z","msg":"軍政府狀態、差佬大撚晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9aa27eb439024e7cbb0b3a9f690cc5ab21ba26","tid":1388600,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWfWePd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWfWePd.png&h=c9a05450&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcY1qVT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcY1qVT.png&h=9521ccf4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m09smue.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm09smue.png&h=fc1b3179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"227ee61ce13ecb8c1328bd7ec390b5017f8cb7e8","tid":1388600,"uid":68822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:39:41.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=c495ab8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kT%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=94b81b46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage"},{"pid":"7ed4ca6272ea98df1026720008c3c12bf55382d8","tid":1388600,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"82遮打集會<br />\n85全民罷工"},{"pid":"93138f56dbd6d2ce64a8cd1cad15759edef255fe","tid":1388600,"uid":271974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:41:54.000Z","msg":"撐."},{"pid":"1de1d77f86671df7c6bbdb310f22f6f15c14670f","tid":1388600,"uid":211565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:42:07.000Z","msg":"軍政府狀態 差佬大撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfc1b9c5b4830f0570bfbba59ce7c969e682dfe","tid":1388600,"uid":198991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0